### ==========================================================
### Health & Infrastructure — 2 requests
### ==========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050

### 1. Gateway aggregated health check (no auth required)
# Returns status of all downstream services (auth, habit, social, challenge, notification, activity)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. NATS monitoring health
# Requires debug compose overlay:
#   docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.debug.yml up
# Port 8222 is the NATS monitoring port (not 4222 which is the client port)
GET http://localhost:8222/healthz
